---
title: "Sweepstakes"
---

**Version Date: February 20, 2025**

This guide outlines the Sweepstakes feature on Rally Engage, where Members can participate in events to win prizes. Rally Engage offers two types of sweepstakes: **Public Sweepstakes**, hosted by the platform for all Members, and **Private Sweepstakes**, customized by clients for specific groups. This document explains participation processes, client customization options, and key user experiences for Members.

---

## **1\. Public Sweepstakes**

**Overview:**

Public Sweepstakes are platform-wide events organized by Rally Engage, accessible to all Members. Rally Engage determines the schedule, prizes, and entry method, providing regular opportunities for participation.

### **Key Features:**

- **Eligibility:** Open to all Members with an eligible Rally Engage account.
- **Entry Method:** Predefined by Rally Engage for each sweepstakes, either
  - **Points Redemption:** Members use Rally Engage points to enter, if specified.
  - **Activity-Based:** Members earn entries by completing tasks (e.g., logging in, surveys), if specified.
- **Prizes:** Rewards are exclusively e-gift cards (e.g., Amazon, Starbucks, Target)—no physical items are offered.
- **Frequency:** Rally Engage sets the timing and frequency of these events.
- **Winner Selection:** An automated, random draw occurs one day after the sweepstakes ends.

**Member Experience:**

- Members find Public Sweepstakes in the “Sweepstakes” section or “Rewards” tab.
- Members follow the predefined entry method (points or activities) and track their entries.
- After the draw, winners receive notifications via email, push notifications, or in-app alerts, with 14 days to claim their e-gift card.

---

## **2\. Private Sweepstakes**

**Overview:**

Private Sweepstakes are exclusive events created by clients for their specific Member groups (e.g., employees or community members). Clients customize the details, including prizes and entry rules, to suit their audience.

### **Client Customization Options:**

This section outlines what clients can configure for Private Sweepstakes.

#### **2.1. General Setup**

- **Timing:**
  - **Start Date:** Clients set the start date and time (e.g., March 1, 2025\)
  - **Duration:** Clients define the length (e.g., 7 days, 30 days).
  - **End Date:** Calculated as Start Date \+ Duration, ending at midnight EST.
- **Details:**
- **Name:** A descriptive title (e.g., “Win a $50 Amazon Gift Card”).
- **Short Description:** A brief summary (e.g., “Enter to win a $50 Amazon e-gift card\!”).
- **Extra Info:** Up to three optional sections (e.g., Terms & Conditions, How to Claim Your Prize).

#### **2.2. Prize Choices**

- **E-Gift Cards:**
  - **Brands:** Options include Amazon, Starbucks, Target, and 200+ other brands.
  - **Value:** Clients set values (e.g., $25, $50, $100), within brand-specific limits.
  - **Winners:** Clients determine the number of winners (e.g., 1, 5, 10).
  - **Delivery:** Rally Engage delivers these digitally via the app after claiming.
- **Physical Gifts:**
  - **Details:** Clients describe the prize (e.g., “A luxury coffee maker”).
  - **Winners:** Clients specify the winner count (e.g., 1, 3).
  - **Delivery:** Clients handle fulfillment using a winner report with names and contact details. _(_
  - _Note: Rally Engage does not ship physical prizes as of February 2025.)_

#### **2.3. Entry Rules**

- **Eligibility:** Restricted to specific groups defined by the client based on their affiliation
- **Entry Method:** Predefined by the client as activity-based—Members earn entries through designated tasks (e.g., logging in, completing activities); points redemption is not available.
- **Limits:**
  - **Max Entries:** Clients cap the total entries per Member.
  - **Frequency:** Clients set how often entries can be earned (e.g., 1 per day, 1 per month).
- **Winning Odds:** Additional entries increase a Member’s chances, but each Member can win only once per sweepstakes. This behavior is consistent between public and private sweepstakes.

**2.4. Winner Process**

- **Draw Timing:** Typically one day after the end date (midnight EST), though clients can choose a custom date.
- **Random Selection:** Fully automated and randomized by the system.
- **Claiming:**
  - Winners have 14 days from the draw to claim via the app (“My Rewards” tab) or website (“Sweepstakes” section).
  - Notifications include email, push alerts, and in-app badges.
  - Unclaimed prizes are forfeited after 14 days, with no redraws.

**Member Experience:**

- Members access Private Sweepstakes relevant to their group in the “Sweepstakes” section.
- Members complete the predefined activity-based tasks, track entries, and check results post-draw.

---

## **3\. Member Participation and User Experience**

### **3.1. User Experience**

This section highlights key interactions Members have with sweepstakes, with placeholders for visual examples.

#### **3.1.1. Finding a Sweepstakes**

- Members discover both Public and Private Sweepstakes in the “Sweepstakes” section or “Rewards” tab on the app or website.
- Public Sweepstakes are open to all, while Private Sweepstakes are visible only to eligible group Members and show up under the Featured Sweepstakes section.
- Each sweepstakes appears as a card with its name, prize, and short description.

_![][image1]![][image2]_

_![][image3]_

#### **3.1.2. Purchasing an Entry with Points**

- For Public Sweepstakes predefined as points-based, Members redeem Rally Engage points to enter.
- The process involves selecting the sweepstakes and confirming the points deduction.
- Private Sweepstakes do not support points redemption, relying solely on activities.

#### **3.1.3. Checking Status and Claiming/Accessing a Prize**

- Members track their progress (total entries and remaining opportunities) on the sweepstakes details page during the event.
- Post-draw, winners see a “You Won\!” status and can claim via the “Claim Prize” button in the app (“My Redeemed Rewards”); non-winners see “Sweepstakes Ended.”

![][image8]![][image9]

- Claimed e-gift cards are accessible digitally; physical prizes (Private Sweepstakes only) are fulfilled by clients.

## **4\. Additional Information**

- **Time Zone:** All timings default to Eastern Standard Time (EST).
- **Single Win Rule:** Members can win only once per sweepstakes, regardless of entry count.
- **Prize Fulfillment:**
  - Public Sweepstakes offer e-gift cards only, delivered digitally by Rally Engage.
  - Private Sweepstakes may include physical prizes, fulfilled by clients (Rally Engage does not ship as of February 2025).

## **5\. Standard Content**

### **Public Sweepstakes \- Default Multiple Entry**

#### **How does it work?**

Exchange your points for an entry to the sweepstake. On the draw date, winners are randomly picked. The more entries you have, the higher the chances of you winning. Hurry up, participate now\!

#### **How to claim a prize?**

Winners are notified via email on the draw date. You can always visit the “My Redeemed Rewards” section to check the status and claim your e-gift card within 14 days of the draw to receive your prize.

#### **Terms and Conditions**

- Sweepstakes are open to eligible Rally Engage Members only. Entries must be submitted before the deadline, and unclaimed prizes are forfeited after 14 days.
- By exchanging your points, you are agreeing to \[\[Rally's Reward Rules\]\]. All third party trademarks and images are the property of their respective owners.
